data.description: Welcome home to the desirable community of Valley View Meadows!  Enjoy the curb appeal when you pull up to this home with its mature landscaping.  Enter into the spacious formal living area with soaring vaulted ceilings and abundant windows to let the natural light stream in.  Adjacent is the well proportioned den.  Looking for your primary bedroom downstairs? You just found it!  The primary bedroom is massive, with a walk in closet, and an additional closet.  The primary bath has been remodeled with elegant tile shower, and dual vessel sinks.  The well appointed kitchen is adjacent to the family room, and leads to the lovely rear patio area with above ground spa.  Upstairs you will find the two guest bedrooms with wonderful mountain views, and the guest bathroom with tub shower combination.  Just add a fresh coat of paint throughout and this home will sparkle and shine!  Check out the amazing pictures, or come see for yourself!
